name: Deleted entry
classes: Acting on the aldehyde or oxo group of donors;
With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
comment: Deleted entry: glutathione-dependent formaldehyde dehydrogenase. This enzyme was classified on the basis of an incorrect reaction. It has been replaced by two enzymes, EC 1.1.1.284, S-(hydroxymethyl)glutathione dehydrogenase and EC 4.4.1.22, S-(hydroxymethyl)glutathione synthase
